  ],
  "remarks": "JSC Shvabe (Shvabe), a holding firm owned by Rostec, specialises in research into and the mass manufacture of optical and laser systems and complexes. Shvabe connects a number of industrial sites and research institutions around Russia, forming the backbone of the country's optical sector. The Shvabe holding carries out the complete cycle of developing cutting-edge optoelectronic and laser technology for Russia's national security. Shvabe also produces and develops optoelectronic and laser systems for the Russian Federation's armed forces.",
